title: Khudobin makes 34 saves, leads Ducks to first win
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: NHL - Yesterday 
Khudobin has 34 saves as Ducks beat Wild 4-1 for 1st win after scoring 1 goal in first 4 games ...
